+// Issue #165: the right-click "馃摝 Archive" action used to be a soft hide
+// (toggle `archived` flag). Users expected real archiving 鈥?a Markdown
+// snapshot they can grep, commit, or share. This module renders the
+// session record to Markdown and writes it under
+// `<workspace>/.deepcopilot/archives/yyyyMMdd-HHmmss-<title>.md`.
+//
+// Edge cases handled:
+//   - No workspace open      鈫?fall back to vscode.window.showSaveDialog.
+//   - Multi-root workspace   鈫?showWorkspaceFolderPick to choose target.
+//   - Path traversal         鈫?resolved path must stay under chosen root
+//                              (defence in depth even though titles are
